<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-10-01T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-10-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="204" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d204">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.13/27.</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Scholle</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-10-01">
                                    <hi rend="italic">October 1, 1914</hi></date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>The House yesterday passed Amnesty Bill for all accused or convicted of
                            murder, attempted murder or assault and battery, providing offender is a
                            veteran of War of Cuban Independence. Further, all accomplices, and
                            those convicted of newspaper libel whether veterans or not. The result
                            of this law will be the liberation of Asbert and Arias: the murderers of
                            General Rivas, Chief of Police of Habana.</p>
                        <p>It is probable that the Senate will act tomorrow.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Scholle</hi></signed>.</closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>